{"tid":740684,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[回帶] 笑星救地球 之 97前後 😁","createTime":"2018-07-13T05:27:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-13T18:39:27.000Z","uid":44730,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3925c7d0c48a718fde83dc4bdf4adba5ab22e80b","tid":740684,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T05:27:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/8rvLzMBRExw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F8rvLzMBRExw&d=D2YYfmw9pscn5chN2XgR%2BghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=6920f433\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/8rvLzMBRExw</a><br />\n<br />\n28年後你地見到有咩字真係出現咗 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/05/130749_f6d79dfbdfb935b547b31d6eec79afed.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F05%2F130749_f6d79dfbdfb935b547b31d6eec79afed.png&h=0657fa5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ebf208c639d0f9d3cf42e35d52f232ae0299b771","tid":740684,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T06:02:44.000Z","msg":"細龜同黃一生拍過套電影個名差唔多，仲喺同年上映<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/13/140124_64825f371dd7a0b738665b7ca5e65808.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F13%2F140124_64825f371dd7a0b738665b7ca5e65808.png&h=6c52c8c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkmdb.com/db/movies/view.mhtml?id=7298&amp;display_set=big5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkmdb.com%2Fdb%2Fmovies%2Fview.mhtml%3Fid%3D7298%26display_set%3Dbig5&d=D2YYfmw9pscn5chN2XgR%2BghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=3781fdd8\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkmdb.com/db/movies/view.mhtml?id=7298&amp;display_set=big5</a>"},{"pid":"2b7173a2c6a40678463c978417d3430a56d972bf","tid":740684,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T06:16:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>細龜同<span style=\"color: red;\">黃一生</span>拍過套電影個名差唔多，仲喺同年上映<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/13/140124_64825f371dd7a0b738665b7ca5e65808.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F13%2F140124_64825f371dd7a0b738665b7ca5e65808.png&h=6c52c8c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkmdb.com/db/movies/view.mhtml?id=7298&amp;display_set=big5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkmdb.com%2Fdb%2Fmovies%2Fview.mhtml%3Fid%3D7298%26display_set%3Dbig5&d=D2YYfmw9pscn5chN2XgR%2BghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=3781fdd8\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkmdb.com/db/movies/view.mhtml?id=7298&amp;display_set=big5</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n打錯，想話黃一飛<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/05/130749_f6d79dfbdfb935b547b31d6eec79afed.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F05%2F130749_f6d79dfbdfb935b547b31d6eec79afed.png&h=0657fa5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fffcb15202b8800d5fd9a46eba681c5e25ac3d3e","tid":740684,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T06:37:44.000Z","msg":"外國勢力真係出現咗 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/05/130749_f6d79dfbdfb935b547b31d6eec79afed.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F05%2F130749_f6d79dfbdfb935b547b31d6eec79afed.png&h=0657fa5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大公報<br />\n2018-02-05&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n﻿黃之鋒只是<span style=\"color: red;\">外國勢力</span>的跳樑小丑/博 梁<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;外國勢力&rdquo;這個詞語，在過往一直被不少香港人誤認為是危言聳聽之詞，這跟原國務院港澳辦副主任陳佐洱早於二○一二年便曾指&ldquo;&lsquo;港獨&rsquo;像病毒一樣蔓延&rdquo;一樣，遭到不合理的輕蔑。然而，當看到十二名美國國會議員日前竟去信挪威的諾貝爾委員會，提名觸發違法&ldquo;佔中&rdquo;的&ldquo;雙學&rdquo;三人黃之鋒、羅冠聰和周永康競逐諾貝爾和平獎，大家還敢斷言&ldquo;外國勢力&rdquo;並不存在嗎？"},{"pid":"87b3b5accebb3b3284d5b60a20add6bdf268ceef","tid":740684,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T10:22:57.000Z","msg":"係咪以前先會敢拎同時事有關既黎做題材，而家唔覺有？<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/04/133211_19a6a9085bc66dde26a8720afef6f892.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F04%2F133211_19a6a9085bc66dde26a8720afef6f892.png&h=e2c59df6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f60d37775174f58e38f2f443818eb14cef9db02e","tid":740684,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T10:46:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/dZU8y2j-TQk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FdZU8y2j-TQk&d=D2YYfmw9pscn5chN2XgR%2BghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=a9fb140c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/dZU8y2j-TQk</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/04/133211_19a6a9085bc66dde26a8720afef6f892.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F04%2F133211_19a6a9085bc66dde26a8720afef6f892.png&h=e2c59df6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7b8a1781e905d8fedea321da013befa2a273ac66","tid":740684,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T10:51:24.000Z","msg":"其實係咪冇人睇過<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/04/133211_19a6a9085bc66dde26a8720afef6f892.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F04%2F133211_19a6a9085bc66dde26a8720afef6f892.png&h=e2c59df6&s={SIZE}\" />，聽講依度d人好年輕"},{"pid":"df102cae1d0145ba3b67c5752bc6764045fe2646","tid":740684,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T11:10:46.000Z","msg":"記得在90年，有一套搞笑系列，名為《笑聲救地球》。內裡有一個環節，叫《九七前後》。現時再回看這段笑片，不禁是可笑，還是唏噓。當年，中港兩地生活水平差異甚大，就連當時的電視節目，也若有反映。"},{"pid":"49826662a86751bb821e2956ab6037d447fb9904","tid":740684,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T11:10:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ZFBLFpSJIHw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FZFBLFpSJIHw&d=D2YYfmw9pscn5chN2XgR%2BghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=19f3a20f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ZFBLFpSJIHw</a><br />\n<br />\n上面這段短片，題目為「牌照打」。&nbsp;今天才第一次看這段片的朋友，您可能會不明短片中的人和事。事實上，在九十年代初，一般大陸人的形象，就是片中人物的那樣：中山裝，不梳頭，把腳放在椅子上。他們所講得的術語，也為港人所笑。"},{"pid":"743d843cfa77215f31c6ecd68c2af83a0795767b","tid":740684,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T11:11:18.000Z","msg":"不過，今時今日，其實有很多本地流行的術語，在當年，也曾被認為是大陸的「方言」，例如「高檔」、「低檔」、「平反」、「小道消息」。在二十年前您不要亂說，因為一說，就會被人竊笑，說您大陸化。"},{"pid":"acf90d2cc3187cc8f76301563f73604282c7bbc7","tid":740684,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T11:11:39.000Z","msg":"不能不佩服當年《九七前後》的編導，從中帶出來的幽默。如當年最經典的，莫過如把九七前的「大哥大」，改為九七後「高幹高」等。"},{"pid":"716bd865a9ae5879b828409c3407b5b2719c37ee","tid":740684,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T11:12:00.000Z","msg":"到了今時今日，銷售業最期待的，是一年一度的黃金週。股民最盼望和喜歡的，是QDII，國內資金自由行，和勢如破竹的國企股。<br />\n<br />\n這些，都是一個時代的幽默，一個時代的反映。也代表港人對九七後充滿憂慮的時空。"},{"pid":"6c6927828c5febcd48843a6a4e0c5f30b61ed197","tid":740684,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T13:27:15.000Z","msg":"個編導可能冇諗到 <em>高幹高</em> 冇可能過到97，睇返以前d片，d機唔夠幾年已經縮咗成倍<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/05/130749_f6d79dfbdfb935b547b31d6eec79afed.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F05%2F130749_f6d79dfbdfb935b547b31d6eec79afed.png&h=0657fa5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fdc757e5208f9139a720424c99184057744b4784","tid":740684,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T13:45:00.000Z","msg":"國產凌凌漆既題材係咪算係同佢比較接近？<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/04/133211_19a6a9085bc66dde26a8720afef6f892.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F04%2F133211_19a6a9085bc66dde26a8720afef6f892.png&h=e2c59df6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a4ca1e37a2e761172807a